text: Delwar Hossain Khan is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Narsingdi-2. ==Career== Khan was elected to parliament from Narsingdi-2 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1988. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:Living people Category:4th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Delwar Hossain Khan
